Package: timestampr
Type: Package
Title: Extract Timestamps from Images and Videos
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Gota", "Yajima",
      email = "wildlife.hunter0712@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides tools for extracting timestamp information from images and 
  videos. The package implements optical character recognition (OCR) to detect and 
  parse various timestamp formats commonly found in media files, including 
  surveillance footage, digital camera outputs, and screen recordings. Supports 
  multiple timestamp formats and offers functions for batch processing of media 
  files.
